Name: Keeping Up With the Kardashians
Title: Doggy Blu's
Desc: Khloé must reconsider her attitude; Kendall's lack of responsibility; Scott's newest vehicle.
LongDescription: Khloé must reconsider her attitude when she sees it rubbing off on her sweet little sister. Kendall's lack of responsibility for her dog leaves her and Kris in a messy situation. Scott reveals his newest luxury vehicle.
